{
  "version": "2.8",
  "name": "KEEL",
  "description": "Freelance Finance OS — Dark mode, deep charcoal #0D1017, electric indigo #4F72FF + warm amber #F5A430. Inspired by Midday.ai on darkmodedesign.com: transaction reconciliation with receipt-matching status badges, time tracking connected to invoicing, AI \"explain the numbers\" insight strips. 5 screens: Overview (cash + txn feed), Pipeline (invoice stages), Time (active timer + bars), Cash Flow (monthly bars + expense breakdown), Tax Reserve (auto-set-aside + quarterly payments).",
